    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <div class="chapter-label">Chapter 4: Eugene Schwartz</div>
            <h1><span class="number-highlight">38</span> Ways to Strengthen Your Headline</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">The art of Verbalization: maximizing the force of your message</p>
        </header>

        <div class="intro-card">
            <h2>What is Verbalization?</h2>
            <p>Eugene Schwartz defines <strong>Verbalization</strong> as the art of increasing the impact of a headline by the way in which it is stated. Once you've determined the content of your headline (the basic appeal), you must determine how to say it to maximize its force.</p>
            
            <p><strong>Verbalization serves three primary purposes:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>It strengthens the claim by making it more vivid or measurable</li>
                <li>It makes the claim fresh by twisting the angle or using narration</li>
                <li>It pulls the prospect into the body copy by partially revealing mechanisms or offering information</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="category-nav">
            <h3>Jump to Category</h3>
            <div class="category-buttons">
                <button class="category-btn" onclick="scrollToCategory('category-1')">Intensifying (1-7)</button>
                <button class="category-btn" onclick="scrollToCategory('category-2')">Modifying Logic (8-15)</button>
                <button class="category-btn" onclick="scrollToCategory('category-3')">Newness & Exclusivity (16-21)</button>
                <button class="category-btn" onclick="scrollToCategory('category-4')">Mechanism & Info (22-28)</button>
                <button class="category-btn" onclick="scrollToCategory('category-5')">Psychological (29-38)</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CATEGORY 1: INTENSIFYING THE CLAIM -->
        <div class="category-section" id="category-1">
            <div class="category-header">
                <div class="category-number">Category One</div>
                <h2 class="category-title">Intensifying the Claim</h2>
                <div class="category-count">Techniques 1‚Äì7</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="techniques-grid">
                <div class="technique-card" data-category="1" data-technique="1">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <div class="technique-num">Technique #01</div>
                        <h3 class="technique-title">Measure the Size of the Claim</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="technique-content">
                        <p class="technique-description">Use specific numbers to provide scale and make your claim tangible and believable.</p>
                        
                        <div class="example-box">
                            <div class="example-label">Classic Example</div>
                            <div class="example-text">"20,000 filter traps in Viceroy"</div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="worksheet">
                            <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline</label>
                            <textarea class="worksheet-input" placeholder="Add a specific number to quantify your benefit..."></textarea>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-category="1" data-technique="2">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <div class="technique-num">Technique #02</div>
                        <h3 class="technique-title">Measure the Speed of the Claim</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="technique-content">
                        <p class="technique-description">Highlight how quickly the product works to create urgency and immediate appeal.</p>
                        
                        <div class="example-box">
                            <div class="example-label">Classic Example</div>
                            <div class="example-text">"Feel better fast"</div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="worksheet">
                            <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline</label>
                            <textarea class="worksheet-input" placeholder="How fast does your product deliver results?"></textarea>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-category="1" data-technique="3">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <div class="technique-num">Technique #03</div>
                        <h3 class="technique-title">Compare the Claim</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="technique-content">
                        <p class="technique-description">Use a comparative standard to show superiority over alternatives or the status quo.</p>
                        
                        <div class="example-box">
                            <div class="example-label">Classic Example</div>
                            <div class="example-text">"Six times whiter washes"</div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="worksheet">
                            <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline</label>
                            <textarea class="worksheet-input" placeholder="What can you compare your product to?"></textarea>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-category="1" data-technique="4">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <div class="technique-num">Technique #04</div>
                        <h3 class="technique-title">Metaphorize the Claim</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="technique-content">
                        <p class="technique-description">Use strong verbs to create a vivid mental image of action and transformation.</p>
                        
                        <div class="example-box">
                            <div class="example-label">Classic Example</div>
                            <div class="example-text">"Melt away ugly fat"</div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="worksheet">
                            <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline</label>
                            <textarea class="worksheet-input" placeholder="What powerful verb captures your benefit?"></textarea>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-category="1" data-technique="5">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <div class="technique-num">Technique #05</div>
                        <h3 class="technique-title">Sensitize the Claim</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="technique-content">
                        <p class="technique-description">Make the prospect feel, smell, touch, see, or hear the benefit through sensory language.</p>
                        
                        <div class="example-box">
                            <div class="example-label">Classic Example</div>
                            <div class="example-text">"The skin you love to touch"</div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="worksheet">
