                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-category="1" data-technique="6">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <div class="technique-num">Technique #06</div>
                        <h3 class="technique-title">Demonstrate with a Prime Example</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="technique-content">
                        <p class="technique-description">Show the product succeeding in a difficult or extreme situation to prove its superiority.</p>
                        
                        <div class="example-box">
                            <div class="example-label">Classic Example</div>
                            <div class="example-text">Fighter fails to flatten a paper cup (demonstrating cup strength)</div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="worksheet">
                            <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline</label>
                            <textarea class="worksheet-input" placeholder="What extreme test could your product pass?"></textarea>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-category="1" data-technique="7">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <div class="technique-num">Technique #07</div>
                        <h3 class="technique-title">Dramatize the Claim or Result</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="technique-content">
                        <p class="technique-description">Use a narrative hook to show the dramatic outcome or transformation.</p>
                        
                        <div class="example-box">
                            <div class="example-label">Classic Example</div>
