                        <h3 class="technique-title">State as a Paradox</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="technique-content">
                        <p class="technique-description">Create intrigue through apparent contradiction that makes readers curious.</p>
                        
                        <div class="example-box">
                            <div class="example-label">Classic Example</div>
                            <div class="example-text">"How a bald-headed barber saved my hair"</div>
